Theme Description

Android was first unveiled on 5 November 2007 was announced with the founding of the Open Handset Alliance, a consortium of 71 hardware, software, and telecom companies devoted to advancing open standards for mobile devices.
Since then Google has taken Android to a whole new level, with several handset models and Android OS have been released since then.

If you are an Android Fan you would love the Android Windows 7 Theme. It consists of 25+ Custom Android Wallpapers, Custom Android Icons and some Funky sounds which every Android fan would appreciate.
